.TH "destroy_worker" 9 "destroy_worker" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
destroy_worker \- destroy a workqueue worker
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" destroy_worker
.BI "(struct worker *worker "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "worker" 12
worker to be destroyed
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Destroy \fIworker\fP and adjust \fIpool\fP stats accordingly.  The worker should
be idle.
.SH "CONTEXT"
raw_spin_lock_irq(pool->lock).
